"title": "5425: net",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5425: net",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Instruments of meshed string, used for fishing or hunting. The term can also be used in a symbolic manner, to refer to the way in which people are ensnared by sin or by their enemies.</p>\n<h2>Nets used in fishing and hunting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:20\">ISA 51:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:10\">EZK 47:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18\">MAT 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:17\">PRO 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:8\">ISA 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:5\">EZK 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:21\">MAT 4:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19\">MRK 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:47\">MAT 13:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:18\">MRK 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:2-Luke5:4\">LUK 5:2–5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:6\">JHN 21:6</a></p>\n<h2>Nets used metaphorically</h2>\n<h3>To describe people being caught by others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:5\">PRO 29:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:15-Hab1:17\">HAB 1:15–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:8\">JOB 18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:15\">PSA 9:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:9\">PSA 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:15\">PSA 25:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:7\">PSA 35:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:6\">PSA 57:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:5\">PSA 140:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:10\">PSA 141:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:8\">EZK 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:1\">HOS 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:2\">MIC 7:2</a></p>\n<h3>To describe being caught by the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:6\">JOB 19:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:12\">HOS 7:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:10\">LUK 5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:13\">LAM 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:13\">EZK 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:20\">EZK 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:3\">EZK 32:3</a></p>\n<h2>Networks used in design</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:4-Exod27:5\">EXO 27:4–27:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:17\">1KI 7:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:22\">JER 52:22</a></p>",
